%^BOLD%^-=%^CYAN%^Cold Domain%^WHITE%^=-%^RESET%^

The cold domain draws upon snow and ice to create 
both protection for the caster and devastating 
effects upon the victim.

The cold domain contains the following spells:
Ice Shield (3rd), Frost Breath (5th), and Hypothermia (7th)

%^CYAN%^Deities%^RESET%^: Lord Shadow

%^BOLD%^Please see individual help files for an explanation of what each spell does.%^RESET%^
     